Introduction

FAINIT is a five-member girl group under FAINIT Company. Their name stands for Fantasy Avatar Intersection Nationality Idol Travel, or To the world of various fantasies (F) characters (A) intersecting between fantasy and reality (I) travelling between various spaces (N) as an idol (I) to a new world (T). This is supposed to represent the initiation of the "FAINIT UNIVERSE" and how the group will link various cultures together through transcending time and space. They made their official debut on June 13, 2022, with the single “KILLER”.

On September 22, 2022, a friend of one of the members revealed that the group had disbanded after not even a month of debuting. Members Liha, Idam, Seoa, and Meanu have joined Chrome Entertainment as trainees, while Jinseo wants to pursue acting instead.
